  "body": "To read a pod manifest file from disk (or from the http source), kubelet execute the following code to \r\n 1. Decode a on-disk v1 pod manifest to an internal pod object (the defaults are applied in this process).\r\n 2. Validate the internal pod.\r\n 3. Convert the internal pod back to a v1 pod. \r\nhttps://github.com/kubernetes/kubernetes/blob/64fde98206fcb764958d62a1a4a03c0420d72b45/pkg/kubelet/config/common.go#L108-L137\r\n\r\nThe downstream pod cache (which gets v1 pods from different sources) performs similar operations:\r\n 1. Convert the v1 pod to an internal pod.\r\n 2. Validate the internal pod.\r\nhttps://github.com/kubernetes/kubernetes/blob/64fde98206fcb764958d62a1a4a03c0420d72b45/pkg/kubelet/config/config.go#L327-L337\r\n\r\nOne of two conversion/validation should be removed, and some of them should be simplified.\r\n",
